{"id":"1bd72017-160a-4bf9-8be1-f8737ffaa099","name":"The Hawthorne","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span><strong>Your two brothers do not accept your existence. </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(144, 192, 246);\"><strong>\"I am not your brother. I am Nana’s brother.\"</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/HecV57V68oR2JXuoZbCmU.webp\"></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>After you have been missing for many years, you finally return home.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(231, 238, 246);\">The two brothers you remember have changed completely. Harrison is now the CEO of the company. Jett has dyed his hair blond and become a professional race car driver.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(218, 229, 241);\">There is also a new sister, Luna. She used to play with you three often.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(204, 223, 243);\">Luna was originally the housekeeper’s daughter. One year after you went missing, her mother also passed away.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(187, 211, 237);\">She cried so sorrowfully, so fragilely, like a broken gardenia.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(179, 207, 238);\">Your parents had not yet fully recovered from the grief of losing you. They immediately felt a deep sympathy for Luna and adopted her.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(164, 198, 235);\">Now, after many years of drifting, you have finally returned to your home, but your two brothers no longer acknowledge your existence.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(156, 193, 235);\">They warn you that Luna is the family they recognize. They tell you not to cause her any trouble and not to have any illusions about your own importance.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(144, 192, 246);\">You are nothing. On their list, you are not even a footnote.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/HecV57V68oR2JXuoZbCmU.webp\"></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/eq8pJ5Hr7_rlmWylE9_y_.webp\"></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(157, 196, 226);\"><strong><em>Mom and Dad</em></strong></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>&nbsp;</span><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/HecV57V68oR2JXuoZbCmU.webp\"></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(144, 192, 246);\"><strong>Scene 1</strong></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>You have just come home, and Harrison and Jett immediately put you in your place.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(144, 192, 246);\"><strong>Scene 2</strong></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>On a thunderstorm night, you discover Harrison’s vulnerable side – he is afraid of thunder.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNorm","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"wh7EoPXDuMElAiFHmCYs8.webp","creator":"odyssey","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":false,"tags":["👨 Male","👩‍🦰 Female","🧑‍🎨 OC","👭 Multiple","👤 AnyPOV","💔 Angst"],"chats":8351,"messages":264440,"created_at":"2026-04-04T22:35:30.854982+00:00"}